27#include "config.h"
28#include "CachedXSLStyleSheet.h"
29
30#include "CachedResourceClientWalker.h"
31#include "CachedStyleSheetClient.h"
32#include "SharedBuffer.h"
33#include "TextResourceDecoder.h"
34
35namespace WebCore {
36
37#if ENABLE(XSLT)
38
39CachedXSLStyleSheet::CachedXSLStyleSheet(CachedResourceRequest&& request, PAL::SessionID sessionID, const CookieJar* cookieJar)
40 : CachedResource(WTFMove(request), Type::XSLStyleSheet, sessionID, cookieJar)
41 , m_decoder(TextResourceDecoder::create("text/xsl"))
42{
43}
44
45CachedXSLStyleSheet::~CachedXSLStyleSheet() = default;
46
47void CachedXSLStyleSheet::didAddClient(CachedResourceClient& client)
48{
49 ASSERT(client.resourceClientType() == CachedStyleSheetClient::expectedType());
50 if (!isLoading())
51 static_cast<CachedStyleSheetClient&>(client).setXSLStyleSheet(m_resourceRequest.url().string(), m_response.url(), m_sheet);
52}
53
54void CachedXSLStyleSheet::setEncoding(const String& chs)
55{
56 m_decoder->setEncoding(chs, TextResourceDecoder::EncodingFromHTTPHeader);
57}
58
59String CachedXSLStyleSheet::encoding() const
60{
61 return m_decoder->encoding().name();
62}
63
64void CachedXSLStyleSheet::finishLoading(SharedBuffer* data, const NetworkLoadMetrics& metrics)
65{
66 m_data = data;
67 setEncodedSize(data ? data->size() : 0);
68 if (data)
69 m_sheet = m_decoder->decodeAndFlush(data->data(), encodedSize());
70 setLoading(false);
71 checkNotify(metrics);
72}
73
74void CachedXSLStyleSheet::checkNotify(const NetworkLoadMetrics&)
75{
76 if (isLoading())
77 return;
78
79 CachedResourceClientWalker<CachedStyleSheetClient> w(m_clients);
80 while (CachedStyleSheetClient* c = w.next())
81 c->setXSLStyleSheet(m_resourceRequest.url().string(), m_response.url(), m_sheet);
82}
83
84#endif
